National Assembly – Question for written reply QUESTION FOR WRITTEN REPLY QUESTION NUMBER: 561 [NW1558E] DATE OF PUBLICATION: 23 AUGUST 2019 561.     Mr D W Macpherson (DA) to ask the Minister of Finance: What amounts for transfer duties on properties were collected in the (a) 2016-17, (b) 2017-18 and (c) 2018-19 financial years? REPLY: Revenue received for Transfer duties on properties were as follows: (a)    2016-17: R8.2bn (b)    2017-18: R7.7bn (c)     2018-19: R7.2bn Issued by Parliament, 11 September 2019